Package: kfreebsd-source-5.3
Architecture: all
Section: devel
Recommends: freebsd5-buildutils (>= 5.3)
Provides: kfreebsd-source-5, kfreebsd-source
Replaces: kfreebsd5-source
Description: source code for kernel of FreeBSD 5.3 with Debian patches
 This package provides the source code for kernel of FreeBSD 5.3, base of 
 a GNU/kFreeBSD system.

Package: kfreebsd-image-5.3-1
Architecture: kfreebsd-i386
Section: base
Essential: yes
Depends: freebsd-utils (>= 5), kldutils
Provides: kfreebsd-image-5, kfreebsd-image
Conflicts: kfreebsd5, kfreebsd-image
Replaces: kfreebsd5
Description: kernel of FreeBSD 5.3 image
 This package provides the binary image and pre-built loadable modules for 
 the kernel of FreeBSD 5.3, base of a GNU/kFreeBSD system.

Package: kfreebsd-headers-5.3-1
Architecture: kfreebsd-i386
Section: devel
Provides: kfreebsd-headers-5, kfreebsd-headers
Depends: coreutils
Description: header files for kernel of FreeBSD 5.3
 This package provides the header files for kernel of FreeBSD 5.3, generally 
 used for building out-of-tree kernel modules. These files are going to be 
 installed into /usr/src/kfreebsd-headers-5.3-1, and can be used for building 
 modules that load into the kernel provided by the kfreebsd-image-5.3-1 package.
      
